oads/2024/08/Catfish-and-the-Bottlemen-perform-at-Leeds-Festival.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2024 年 8 月 23 日，Catfish and the Bottlemen 乐队的 Van McCann 在 2024 年利兹音乐节第一天在英国利兹布拉默姆公园的主舞台上表演。图片来源：马修·贝克/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Catfish-and-the-Bottlemen-perform-at-Leeds-Festival.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Catfish-and-the-Bottlemen-perform-at-Leeds-Festival.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Catfish-and-the-Bottlemen-perform-at-Leeds-Festival.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Catfish-and-the-Bottlemen-perform-at-Leeds-Festival.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Catfish-and-the-Bottlemen-perform-at-Leeds-Festival.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Catfish-and-the-Bottlemen-perform-at-Leeds-Festival.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>昨晚（8 月 23 日） <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/catfish-and-the-bottlemen">，Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen</a>成为利兹音乐节的头条新闻。这是他们玩过的所有内容。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-liveblog-news-updates-reviews-rumours-photo-video-3785825">Reading &amp; Leeds 2024 直播博客：所有发生的动作</a></strong></li></ul><p>乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-six-headliners-revealed-as-first-wave-of-line-up-announced-tickets-3548085">第二次成为雷丁和利兹音乐节的主角</a>，并将于明天（8 月 25 日星期日）晚上 8:10 在雷丁的主舞台上演出。</p><p>在周末最受期待的表演之一中，主唱范·麦肯 (Van McCann) 为歌迷带来了一张包含三张专辑中热门歌曲的歌单，让歌迷们大饱眼福。威尔士乐队以《Longshot》拉开了他们的演出序幕，随后是《Kathleen》和《Soundcheck》。</p><p>随后，他们演奏了《Twice》、《Homesick》和《Outside》，然后带领歌迷合唱了取自 2016 年专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-catfish-and-the-bottlemen-16481-305848">The Ride</a> 》的《7》，充满活力。播放的大部分曲目来自他们 2014 年的首张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-various-artists-15657-324542">Balcony</a> 》，包括更接近的歌曲《Cocoon》</p><p>请查看下面的曲目列表和他们的表演片段。</p><h3> <strong>Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen&#39;s 利兹音乐节 2024 年曲目列表为：</strong></h3><p> <strong>“远射”</strong><br /> <strong>“凯瑟琳”</strong><br /> <strong>“声音检查”</strong><br /> <strong>“奶嘴”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;两次&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;掉出来&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;对话&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;想家&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>“2全部”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;兰戈&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;外部&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;波动&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>‘7’</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;茧&#39;</strong></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">鲶鱼和装瓶商今天在利兹唱茧<br />我很激动<a href="https://t.co/jSQij92lkq">pic.twitter.com/jSQij92lkq</a></p><p> — 玛哈 |看到乔斯特!!!.€:):) <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/26bd.png" alt="⚽" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f54a.png" alt="🕊" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> （@waveyfingdavey） <a href="https://twitter.com/waveyfingdavey/status/1827087262557073561?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 8 月 23 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">利兹音乐节上的CATB！！！ <a href="https://t.co/CjkjVMePe0">pic.twitter.com/CjkjVMePe0</a></p><p> - 鲶鱼和装瓶工档案 (@catbfiles) <a href="https://twitter.com/catbfiles/status/1827079584661000683?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 8 月 23 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="7 - 鲶鱼和装瓶工在 2024 年利兹音乐节现场演出" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LbLUU7R1vSY?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen 宣布携复出单曲《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-the-bottlemen-share-comeback-single-showtime-and-announce-more-uk-headline-shows-3591486">Showtime</a> 》回归，该乐队此前曾在二月份在其社交媒体频道上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-post-clip-of-first-new-music-in-five-years-3589012">发布了一段 6 秒的曲目片段来调侃这首</a>歌曲。乐队还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-the-bottlemen-announce-7-inch-and-merch-for-new-single-showtime-back-to-the-graft-again-3590146">发布了预购的 7 英寸白色黑胶唱片《Showtime》以及新商品</a>。</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-the-bottlemen-release-rare-bonus-track-asa-from-the-balcony-10th-anniversary-reissue-3776175">乐队分享了即将发行的《The Balcony》十周年纪念版的附赠曲目《ASA》。</a>该曲目最初于 2013 年作为《Rango》的 B 面发行。</p><p>这支威尔士乐队正准备纪念他们开创性的首张专辑发行十周年。再版将于 9 月 16 日发售 - 请<a href="https://catb.lnk.to/TB10collectionWE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订。</p><p>除了《ASA》之外，《The Balcony》及其十周年再版也将收录<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-22-1222666">Ewan McGregor 翻唱的《Hourglass》</a> 、《Rango》（单曲版）和其他三首额外曲目。</p><p>此外，还将推出限量版7英寸单曲盒装，仅限购买2,000张。</p><p>他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-announce-first-sadium-shows-in-england-and-wales-for-summer-2025-3784801">还宣布了他们的首次体育场巡演</a>，将于 2025 年 8 月开始。门票现已发售，您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fcatfish-and-the-bottlemen-tickets%2Fartist%2F5121447" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买。 </p><figure id="attachment_3774334" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3774334" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3774334" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024.jpg" alt="鲶鱼和装瓶工（图片来源：Charlie Barclay Harris）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/CATB-Band-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3774334" class="wp-caption-text">鲶鱼和装瓶工（图片来源：Charlie Barclay Harris）</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024">2024 年雷丁和利兹音乐节</a>于昨天（8 月 23 日）在里奇菲尔德大道（雷丁）和布拉汉姆公园（利兹）的惯常地点拉开帷幕 –<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-how-to-watch-online-and-at-home-3785021">请参阅此处</a>，了解如何在家中通过 BBC iPlayer 和其他地方观看音乐节（如果您无法观看）确保获得门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fred-again">Fred Again..</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">Liam Gallagher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/catfish-and-the-bottlemen">Catfish And The Bottlemen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blink-182">Blink-182</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gerry-cinnamon">Gerry Cinnamon</a>是今年音乐节的六大主角。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">雷伊</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">,</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c"> </a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/spiritbox">Spiritbox</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-d-c">Fontaines DC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/renee-rapp">Reneé Rapp</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pendulum">Pendulum</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/denzel-curry">Denzel Curry</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kenny-beats">Kenny Beats</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nia-archives">Nia Archives</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/two-door-cinema-club">Two Door Cinema Club</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Neck-Deep">Neck Deep</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-wombats">The Wombats</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rachel-chinouriri">Rachel Chinouriri</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hak-baker">Hak Baker</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">The Last Evening Party</a>等也有望参演。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-leeds-festival-2024"><i>请返回 NME，</i></a><i>了解雷丁和利兹 2024 年的最新新闻、评论、采访、照片等。</i></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/leeds-festival-2024-heres-what-catfish-the-bottlemen-played-3786661">2024 年利兹音乐节后：这就是 Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen 演奏的内容，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
